text: Philipp Buhl (born 19 December 1989) is a German competitive sailor. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's Laser class. He finished in 14th place. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:German sailors Category:Olympic sailors of Germany Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Laser
